🧑‍💼 ADMIN / STAFF / TEACHER FLOW
✅ 5. Create Admin / Staff / Teacher (By Super Admin)

TO-DO

Create user with:

username starts with MFM (example: MFM_ADMIN_01)

role assigned

email required

Generate temporary password

Save temp password hash + expiry (24 hours)

Send temp password via EMAIL or SMS

Mark isFirstLogin = true

✅ 6. First Login with Temporary Password

TO-DO

Login using username + temp password

Validate temp password + expiry

Force password change

Save new password (bcrypt)

Mark isFirstLogin = false

Invalidate temp password

