Block route access at backend level (not only UI)

✅ 8. Forgot Password (Admin / Staff / Teacher)

Flow

Enter username

System finds linked email

Generate OTP

Send OTP via Nodemailer

Verify OTP

Allow new password creation

Hash & save password

Invalidate OTP

TO-DO

OTP expires in 5 minutes

Max retry limit (security)

Same flow reused for Parents

